oth phases. Our\nresults further indicate enhanced magnetic fluctuations in the pressure induced\nAFM2 phase. The experimental observations together with density functional\ntheory calculations suggest that the magnetic and structural order parameters\nin LuFe$_4$Ge$_2$ are linked by magnetic frustration, causing the simultaneous\nmagneto-structural transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2023 17:44:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-24"}
