 compact discs. Here, the optimum values of the $\\alpha$ viscosity parameter\nlie between $3\\times10^{-4}$ and $10^{-3}$ and with internal photoevaporation\nbeing the main mode of disc dispersal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2023 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2023 12:20:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
