y cusps. If it is\nindeed dark matter annihilation radiation, then prompt cusps in the outer\nGalactic halo and beyond must account for 20-80% of the observed isotropic\n$\\gamma$-ray background in the 1 to 10 GeV range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2023 19:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2023 16:10:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
