etic Weyl semimetals NdAl$X$, but transport properties including AHE are\naffected by material-specific extrinsic effects such as disorders, despite the\npresence of prominent Berry curvature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2023 09:22:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Mar 2023 00:37:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
