$ when the magnetic\nfields of the planet and star are aligned. In case of lower efficiency factors\nthe magnetospheric emission scenario is according to the parameter space\nmodeled in this study not powerful enough. In case of a magnetic polarity\nreversal of the host star towards an anti-aligned field configuration, expected\nradio powers in the magnetospheric emission scenario fall below the observable\nthreshold.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2023 13:43:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
